                             "language_id":  89,
                             "slug":  "kurd-tafsir-rebar",
                             "translated_name":  {
                                                     "name":  "Rebar Kurdish Tafsir",
                                                     "language_name":  "english"
                                                 },
                             "text":  "[ \u003cspan class=\"arabic uthmani\"\u003eمَا الْقَارِعَةُ (٢)\u003c/span\u003e ] ئه‌ی محمد - \u003cspan class=\"saw\"\u003eصلی الله علیه وسلم\u003c/span\u003e - تۆ چوزانی (قاریعه‌) چیه‌؟"
                         },
                   "3":  {
